%table.center
  %caption
    %p.wide
      You are much more sensitive to stimulation.
      %br
      You feel like you have much more energy.
      %br
      Despite consuming less, you produce more.
  %tr
    %th Irritable Mania
    %th Euphoric Mania
  %tr
    %td.half
      %p
        In Consumption realms, mania feels bad.
        %br
        Objectively, it has a good effect.
    %td.half
      %p
        In Production realms, mania feels good.
        %br
        Objectively, it has a bad effect.
  -subtypes.in_groups_of(2) do |row|
    %tr
      -row.each do |subtype|
        %td.half=render "mania", :subtype => subtype
